168
00:08:29,467 --> 00:08:33,263
“Auribus oculi fideliores sunt” 怎麼樣了

169
00:08:34,014 --> 00:08:37,142
Auribus oculi fideliores sunt

170
00:08:37,267 --> 00:08:39,477
Auribus oculi fideliores su...

171
00:08:40,020 --> 00:08:42,981
Auribus oculi fideliore...s

172
00:08:43,732 --> 00:08:46,693
“Auribus oculi fideliores sunt”

173
00:08:47,277 --> 00:08:49,612
“Auribus oculi fideliores sunt”

174
00:08:50,363 --> 00:08:53,158
是 “Auribus oculi fideliores sunt”

175
00:08:54,367 --> 00:08:56,578
“Auribus oculi fideliores sunt”

176
00:08:56,786 --> 00:08:57,912
哦~~

177
00:08:59,164 --> 00:09:01,583
事情變麻煩了呢

178
00:09:02,167 --> 00:09:04,127
怎麼看都是吃多了呢

179
00:09:04,627 --> 00:09:09,466
總之過量攝入了比學園都市規定量要高的食物

180
00:09:10,341 --> 00:09:11,718
就會變成這樣

181
00:09:12,761 --> 00:09:14,721
在那之後、平安無事地回去了
